#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Ofte spurte spørsmål"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Eg har lyst til å endra korleis spelet ser ut. Kan eg det?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>No.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Nei.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Kan eg bruka tastaturet til å spela?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kollision; can only be played with a mouse."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Eg forstår ikkje kva eg skal gjera. Finst det hint?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kollision; does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Eg må slutta å spela no, men eg er ikkje ferdig. Kan eg lagra spelet og "
"komma attende til det seinare?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "You cannot save games in &kollision;."
msgstr ""

